    - textId: 561
      textValue: Update failed. Please try again!
    - textId: 562
      textValue: Network error. Please try again!
    - textId: 563
      textValue: No internet connection. Please try again!
    - textId: 564
      textValue: Network error!
    - textId: 565
      textValue: Please connect to the internet and reopen the game
    - textId: 566
      textValue: A stable network connection is recommended to ensure smooth gameplay and prevent data loss.
    - textId: 567
      textValue: Sign in to Game Center or Google Play Games to ensure your progress is always backed up securely.
    - textId: 568
      textValue: Did you know? Signing in to Game Center or Google Play Games lets you team up with others and join special events without any interruptions.
    - textId: 569
      textValue: Complete all of the shipper's orders to successfully pass the level.
    - textId: 570
      textValue: Support your team by donating up to 3 cards a day! It’s the fastest way to help everyone finish their card collections.
    - textId: 571
      textValue: Need a card? You can request one card from your team every day to help finish your collection quickly!
    - textId: 572
      textValue: Got a duplicate card? Don't worry! They turn into Star Points which you can use to get new card packs and complete your collection.
    - textId: 573
      textValue: Accidentally lost your progress? Use the Data Synchronization feature in Settings to recover your game data.
    - textId: 574
      textValue: Join the Foodie Sizzle Facebook group to get the latest updates, chat with fellow players, and share your achievements with the community!
    - textId: 575
      textValue: Keep your network stable to make sure your Hearts refill without interruption.
    - textId: 576
      textValue: Don't worry if you have to exit the game unexpectedly! Just ensure a stable connection, and you can pick up right where you left off.
    - textId: 577
      textValue: Ads not loading? Check your internet connection and restart the game to claim your rewards.
    - textId: 578
      textValue: When a shipper requests an order with chili, place the skewers on the red-hot grill to finish the order as quickly as possible!
    - textId: 579
      textValue: Enjoy Foodie Sizzle to the fullest! Buy the 'Remove Ads' pack in the Shop to disable interruptive ads.
    - textId: 580
      textValue: Don't forget to claim your Daily Reward! These extra Gold and Boosters will help you finish levels in no time.
    - textId: 581
      textValue: No more ads available for today. Please try again tomorrow.
    - textId: 582
      textValue: Error logging into Game Center. Please verify your network connection and account settings, then retry.
    - textId: 583
      textValue: Error logging into Google Play Game. Please verify your network connection and account settings, then retry.
    - textId: 584
      textValue: Your local progress is already synced with the server.
